{"tid":2323063,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[九灣時代內部裝修重開] 食完真係屌一聲","createTime":"2020-12-13T01:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T08:55:20.000Z","uid":182895,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"022e37723c35ea69502cc4460bdc0c87289d96ba","tid":2323063,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T01:00:05.000Z","msg":"原來之前九龍灣時代冰室內部裝修係<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">擴充營業</span></span><br />\n<br />\n見到黃店成功即刻開胃晒<br />\n於是諗住食豐富啲<br />\n第一次叫厚切豬扒麵<br />\n哇好大塊又勁Juicy<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Trj8gjy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrj8gjy.png&h=d5898137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日終於唔係叫太陽蛋<br />\n又係勁大份, 入邊冇精液但有蛋汁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCrbd6v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCrbd6v.png&h=45739529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n凍飲41蚊<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">屌</span></span>,點解我之前要比多啲錢去對面食透明精液太陽蛋兼受氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXrOgkw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXrOgkw.jpg&h=fb49c50d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd50cea8aa1ab9c2bfb73eefb49513682e29c8c7","tid":2323063,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T01:02:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9035acddcdd423317b2e4f09f3effb7c3ef81d94","tid":2323063,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3817fc22a5c9b3b8940bf22d13a370da2154a9c6","tid":2323063,"uid":118754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T01:15:13.000Z","msg":"過淘大個邊食"},{"pid":"b855131717144f7c112cd3191b0f209f8e2ad8f2","tid":2323063,"uid":94490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"留名先"},{"pid":"ab377c7b53346264c8ee853243ffbfd0058a1e82","tid":2323063,"uid":94490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"scor